item.title: shinkansen home
item.description: 14:37 Tuesday 25 December 2016 JST (written 10:37 Tuesday 27 December 2016 JST) We took the bullet train home. So much faster than the bus! No electrical outlet on this particular train though, so I didn’t write anything on my computer. But I did take a ton of pictures, not all of which I will post here. Or should I? Hmmmmm. 10:57 Okay I pulled them all down from my camera (via https://photos.
